        h2 What you'll need
        p Students will need a 90-day visa to account for the 12-week course. They will also need to book their own flights to Amsterdam. Students are expected to find a suitable housing option for the duration of their stay. NYCDA will provide a list of possible housing options upon contact if needed. Students must have up-to-date vaccinations before leaving for Amsterdam.
        p A Mac or PC laptop. We'll help you get it set up with all of the software required.
        p The motivation and drive to complete an intense, full-time curriculum.
