        h2 Weather

        p Weather in Amsterdam is cool and brisk throughout the year. August is the hottest month in Amsterdam with an average temperature of 17°C (63°F) and the coldest is January at 3°C (37°F) with the most daily sunshine hours at 11 in June. The wettest month is November with an average of 90mm of rain. Expect average temperatures of 10°C (50°F) throughout your stay.
    .content-area.white
      .content.info
        h2 Safety

        p Amsterdam is one of the top 25 safest cities in the world, with a much lower crime rate than many other popular European capitals. In large parts of the city, there are always at least a few people out and about, no matter whether it's Saturday night or Wednesday 3am in the morning.
        p Students should be advised of dangers such as:
        ul
          li Pickpockets
          li Bag/Phone snatchers
          li Getting hit by bikes
          li Getting hit by trams
          li Drugs and alcohol
